              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": " subscriber since 2016, when the Brexit vote made it plain to me that I didn't understand the UK right, and it was about time I did. Reading the ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 2,
                "mode": "normal",
